headline: 5 Dividend Stocks That Motley Fool Experts Are Watching Right Now
summary: In today's uncertain economic landscape, dividend stocks can serve as anchors in your portfolio.  Here are five of their favorite dividend stocks across multiple industries, ranging from real estate investment trusts (REITs) to energy and healthcare.
